name: MEMEFIGHTERS [1/300] - DOGE vs PEPE - Series 22, Card 11 (Rare Pepe)
description:
DOGE vs PEPE. Two memes enter, only one survives. Watch it live on CoinMarketCap.

MEMEFIGHTERS is Series 22, Card 11 of the iconic Rare Pepe Wallet set [1 of 300]. This legendary collection of NFTs was minted on Counterparty (XCP) in 2016-18, long before the barrage of normie NFTs that we see today. Many Counterparty wallets have been lost over the years, thus circulation is likely far lower than stated. Inspect the goods:

https://xchain.io/asset/MEMEFIGHTERS

Counterparty assets live in the OP_RETURN section of the Bitcoin blockchain and are traded via the XCP Dex.



View contents of NFT by expanding Properties Below and at Emblem.Finance 👇

[View this NFT on Emblem.Finance](https://emblem.finance/nft?id=35933822172373081)
